# plugin: prove
# Registry of all skills, agents, and commands in this plugin.
# Used by the commit skill to derive valid scopes.
#
# Format: type | name | path | description
# Types: skill, agent, command

skill   | brainstorm         | skills/brainstorm/         | Interactive brainstorming and decision recording
skill   | task-planner       | skills/task-planner/       | Iterative discovery and planning for tasks
skill   | plan-step          | skills/plan-step/          | Deep-dive requirements for individual plan steps
skill   | orchestrator       | skills/orchestrator/       | Autonomous execution with validation gates
skill   | cleanup            | skills/cleanup/            | Archive artifacts and remove working files
skill   | commit             | skills/commit/             | Semantic commits scoped to plugin items
agent   | principal-architect | agents/                   | Architectural review for orchestrator full mode
command | plan-task          | commands/plan-task.md      | Start task planning session
command | plan-step          | commands/plan-step.md      | Plan a specific step from TASK_PLAN.md
command | autopilot          | commands/autopilot.md      | Run orchestrator in autopilot mode
command | full-auto          | commands/full-auto.md      | Run orchestrator end-to-end from idea to code
command | task-cleanup       | commands/task-cleanup.md   | Clean up task artifacts with archiving
command | commit             | commands/commit.md         | Semantic commit assistant
